{
  "stem": "12003.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when I came to this country, I felt that people didn't know much about what I lived through, what all the survivors lived through.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I was invited somewhere, I was trying to cover up my tattoo.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was introduced to Max Factor stick makeup, but this didn't work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I went to a formal college ball, they gave me long gloves.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I never took my left glove off.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never took my gloves off, period.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For some reason, I was ashamed of my tattoo.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was ashamed of what I went through.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I saw a teenagers that lived such a normal, progressive life, and how much I lost.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I never went through a teenage life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I never went through the moods that-- that the teenagers go through now, that I look at and I said, where was I?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Yes, I-- I did think of removing it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It would have have to be, I guess, a plastic surgery, which I would never do.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And actually, now I just was gonna live as long as I can with it, and die.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's my identification from my childhood.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, I was sent with the group.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, they count you out, and these groups go here and these groups go there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By the way, my aunt was with me, counted out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were trying to be close to each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were-- supposedly we went-- we lived in Birkenau in those barracks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we used to go to work to the Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were brick buildings.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we use to fold and sort out linens.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
